{"title":"Contact","markdown":{"yaml":{"title":"Contact"},"headingText":"Contact Institute 53","containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\n::: {.hero-section style=\"min-height: 40vh;\"}\n::: {.hero-content}\n[GET IN TOUCH]{.hero-label}\n\n\nWe'd love to hear from you.\n:::\n:::\n\n::: {.section-intro}\n::: {.container}\n## Connect With Us\n\nWhether you're a researcher, potential collaborator, or simply want to learn more about our work, we welcome your inquiry.\n\n::: {.pillars-grid}\n::: {.pillar-card}\n##### Headquarters\n\n53 Research Way  \nKendall Square  \nCambridge, MA 02142  \nUnited States\n:::\n\n::: {.pillar-card}\n##### Contact\n\n**Email:** global@institute53.org  \n**Phone:** +1 (617) 555-0153  \n**Fax:** +1 (617) 555-0154\n:::\n\n::: {.pillar-card}\n##### Follow Us\n\nConnect with Institute 53 on social media for the latest research updates, events, and news.\n\n[Facebook](https://facebook.com) | [LinkedIn](https://linkedin.com) | [X](https://x.com)\n:::\n:::\n:::\n:::\n\n::: {.section-translation}\n::: {.container}\n## General Inquiries\n\nFor general inquiries, partnership proposals, or media requests, please email us at **global@institute53.org**. Our team typically responds within 2-3 business days.\n\nFor educational program applications, visit our [Education](education.qmd) page.\n\nFor collaboration opportunities, visit our [Collaborate](collaborate.qmd) page.\n:::\n:::\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":"\n\n::: {.hero-section style=\"min-height: 40vh;\"}\n::: {.hero-content}\n[GET IN TOUCH]{.hero-label}\n\n# Contact Institute 53\n\nWe'd love to hear from you.\n:::\n:::\n\n::: {.section-intro}\n::: {.container}\n## Connect With Us\n\nWhether you're a researcher, potential collaborator, or simply want to learn more about our work, we welcome your inquiry.\n\n::: {.pillars-grid}\n::: {.pillar-card}\n##### Headquarters\n\n53 Research Way  \nKendall Square  \nCambridge, MA 02142  \nUnited States\n:::\n\n::: {.pillar-card}\n##### Contact\n\n**Email:** global@institute53.org  \n**Phone:** +1 (617) 555-0153  \n**Fax:** +1 (617) 555-0154\n:::\n\n::: {.pillar-card}\n##### Follow Us\n\nConnect with Institute 53 on social media for the latest research updates, events, and news.\n\n[Facebook](https://facebook.com) | [LinkedIn](https://linkedin.com) | [X](https://x.com)\n:::\n:::\n:::\n:::\n\n::: {.section-translation}\n::: {.container}\n## General Inquiries\n\nFor general inquiries, partnership proposals, or media requests, please email us at **global@institute53.org**. Our team typically responds within 2-3 business days.\n\nFor educational program applications, visit our [Education](education.qmd) page.\n\nFor collaboration opportunities, visit our [Collaborate](collaborate.qmd) page.\n:::\n:::\n"},"formats":{"html":{"identifier":{"display-name":"HTML","target-format":"html","base-format":"html"},"execute":{"fig-width":7,"fig-height":5,"fig-format":"retina","fig-dpi":96,"df-print":"default","error":false,"eval":true,"cache":null,"freeze":false,"echo":true,"output":true,"warning":true,"include":true,"keep-md":false,"keep-ipynb":false,"ipynb":null,"enabled":null,"daemon":null,"daemon-restart":false,"debug":false,"ipynb-filters":[],"ipynb-shell-interactivity":null,"plotly-connected":true,"engine":"markdown"},"render":{"keep-tex":false,"keep-typ":false,"keep-source":false,"keep-hidden":false,"prefer-html":false,"output-divs":true,"output-ext":"html","fig-align":"default","fig-pos":null,"fig-env":null,"code-fold":"none","code-overflow":"scroll","code-link":false,"code-line-numbers":false,"code-tools":false,"tbl-colwidths":"auto","merge-includes":true,"inline-includes":false,"preserve-yaml":false,"latex-auto-mk":true,"latex-auto-install":true,"latex-clean":true,"latex-min-runs":1,"latex-max-runs":10,"latex-makeindex":"makeindex","latex-makeindex-opts":[],"latex-tlmgr-opts":[],"latex-input-paths":[],"latex-output-dir":null,"link-external-icon":false,"link-external-newwindow":true,"self-contained-math":false,"format-resources":[],"noteboo